<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>From what I understand, if the critter you are fighting bugs out, and gets away, as long as it is still targetted you cast flare and the flare heads right for the beastie, and you can follow the flare in and complete the whacking process, without letting said beastie have the time to fully regen.  I still wouldn't waste a spell slot on it.</font></td></tr></table>
